snippet.title: Sonic R (PC) - Grand Prix: Regal Ruin Gameplay Playthrough
snippet.description:
Sonic R (1998)
Genre: Racing
Platform: PC
Developer: Traveller's Tales
Publisher: Sega

Playing Sonic R, getting all emeralds and coins and beating all challenges to unlock hidden characters. No commentary. Check playlist in the end of description and see all the playthrough.

0:18 - Chaos Emerald (Playing as Tails Doll)
2:24 - Chaos Emerald (Playing as Knuckles)
4:56 - Coins
7:01 - Eggrobo Challenge

Playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL_YL558gxlL_CglV4EXj0VFzWvsX9FxGq
